<cell id="cell-4"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type>## 1 — Download TUM-VI `room1`</cell id="cell-4">
<cell id="cell-5">SEQUENCE     = "room1"
N_FRAMES     = 40
DOWNLOAD_DIR = "/tmp/tumvi"

ds   = TUMVIDataset(sequence=SEQUENCE, n_frames=N_FRAMES, download_dir=DOWNLOAD_DIR)
